==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ea
<hw>Ea</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the Akkadian god of
wisdom; son of Apsu and father of Marduk; counterpart of the Sumerian
Enki.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the Babylonian god of waters and one of the supreme
triad including Anu and Bel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Each</ent>⟦br⟧
